    public class HW5_zfergus2
extends HW4_zfergus2
implements java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.awt.event.MouseWheelListener
    HW05 of CS451 Computer Graphics: Draws 3d objects bouncing in a box and off one another with a directional light and a movable point light. Controls: Move Light in XY Plane: Move Mouse OR Arrow Keys Move Light in Z: Enter and Shift OR Drag Mouse in Y Change Light Intensity: Mouse Wheel OR W and S Change Light Intensity to Value: Number Keys
    Author:
    Zachary Ferguson
